snippet.title: Deep Dive Series - Operators, Gadgets, React Tech | Rainbow Six Extraction
snippet.description:
In Rainbow Six Extraction Deep Dive Series, you'll discover the many specifities of the game. 

In this first episode, you'll learn more about the Operators: who are they, what unique gadgets do they bring to the fight, how the weapons and REACT tech that you choose change the way you play and what kind of perks and upgrades can you unlock to make these Operators more versatile and effective than ever?

Tom Clancy's Rainbow Six Extraction will be available on 20th January 2022 on PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Xbox Series X | S, Xbox One, Stadia and PC.
For more info: 
www.rainbowsixextraction.com
